{"type": "article", "id": 27626, "title": "极简衣帽架", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-01T06:57:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133355NXmOUqkvIB4W7VE9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你喜欢极简风格的衣帽架，由中国工作室 <a href=\"http://en.neriandhu.com/index.html\">Neri&amp;Hu</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.offecct.se/\">Offecct</a> 所设计的 Mr O hanger 会让你眼前一亮。金属经过弯曲后构成了长方形的纤细框架，由下方混凝土制成的底座支撑，在视觉上形成了鲜明的对比。框架的弧线设计减少了金属材质所带来的冰冷的感觉，看上去非常优雅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133353pQdaoibkS9DsLOj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133353Ws98yciPGfu0zMk7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133353aYBOR6fIbGEymVh5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00138889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133354jEYyVN2dFs3mLRKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}